title: This Charming Man - Every Little Secret EP
description:
This Charming Man - Every Little Secret EP (2005). Ripped and encoded as mp3 at 320kbps.

Bought several years back and uploaded simply because I could not find it anywhere else. If you're a fan of the Gaslight Anthem, this is essentially the prototype band.

Track Listing:
1) Bleeder
2) There is a Thunder (Out in the Distance)
3) Sometimes You Eat the Bar (Sometimes the Bar Eats You)
4) Cut the Rope (Before it Hands Us Both)*
5) Kiss Me, I'm a Pirate
6) Sweet Delta Blues

*= Maybe typo but the iTunes listing lists it as "hands." 

Seed and enjoy!
